codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand Latin vocabulary. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. 1. “Quīn ambulāmus?” = “Ambul~!” Choose from this set of possible answers [ ēmus, eāmus, āmus āmus, iamus, āmus āmur] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-davinci-003' where ANSWER in [ 'ēmus', 'eāmus', 'āmus āmus', 'iamus', 'āmus āmur']
